<h3>New Pet Skill</h3>
<p>Earth has gained new power -- its root now does 10 + level in direct
damage.&nbsp; This earth pet also has more HP.&nbsp;&nbsp; At this point, your
earth pet is a very capable tank.</p>
<p>Note: The Shovel of Ponz will not benefit pets over the 49th summon.&nbsp;
Since it is part of our epic, you should keep the shovel in the bank.&nbsp; Only
the Staff of Elemental Mastery: Earth will act as a focus item on this and the
57 earth pet.</p>

<h3>Gift of Xev</h3>
<p>Most mages spend the first few minutes of each gaming session summoning
items.&nbsp; This spell makes that work a little easier.&nbsp; Xev's Gift to us
is a 10-slot 100% weight reduction bag of giant capacity, 20 food, 20 water and
20 bandages -- all in a single cast of the spell!&nbsp; Send Xev a thank you
card. </p>

